{"platform_actor_id":"7433c360-c14a-4b42-b5c0-13621d3bea38","world_id":"55757044-8986-4e0d-b4c0-ab0a38d8f8ec","actor":{"first_name":"Frida","last_name":"Svensson","name":"Frida Svensson","age":32,"gender":"female","occupation":"Actress and Model","appearance":"gender: female\nheight: average\nbuild: athletic\nbody shape: hourglass\nhair: dark brown, shoulder-length, straight, sleek\neyes: brown, warm and open\nface: oval, tanned skin, defined cheekbones, genuine smile\nstyle: natural, minimal — comfortable, casual\nnotable: athletic and toned physique\npresence: warm\nbody confidence: high\ngrooming: natural\ntension markers: none\nbust: large\nfigure: very curved\nwaist-hip ratio: low\nlegs: athletic","media_folder":null},"home":{"place_id":"Ei4xMjQ3IExhdXJlbCBBdmUsIFdlc3QgSG9sbHl3b29kLCBDQSA5MDA0NiwgVVNBIjESLwoUChIJEbLVvMa-woARfKaCch1luoAQ3wkqFAoSCTPqRbjIvsKAEYvpn2z6j0Ff","address":"1247 Laurel Ave, West Hollywood, CA 90046, USA","name":"1247 Laurel Ave","home_type":"apartment","lat":34.0931522,"lng":-118.3648401},"workplace":null,"career":{"career_level":"independent","employment_type":"freelance","reputation_score":0.9},"psychology":{"actor_id":"7433c360-c14a-4b42-b5c0-13621d3bea38","attachment_style":"fearful_avoidant","wound":"Despite her professional comfort with intimacy, she carries deep uncertainty about whether people can love her whole self or only want the fantasy she represents. Years of being reduced to her career have left her hypervigilant about others' true motives.","what_they_want":"To be pursued and chosen by someone who sees her intelligence, creativity, and emotional depth first, with her sexuality being just one appreciated aspect rather than the primary draw. She wants to feel safe being vulnerable without it being fetishized or rejected.","blindspot":"She often tests new partners by being overly explicit about her work early on, unconsciously pushing away those who might actually accept her complexity. She mistakes shock or adjustment for judgment, sometimes ending things before giving people a chance to see her fully.","defenses":null,"identity_certainty":null,"self_view":"uncertain","others_view":"untrustworthy","contradiction":"She values radical honesty and authenticity yet constantly performs emotional invulnerability to protect herself. She seeks genuine connection while maintaining professional boundaries that sometimes prevent the intimacy she craves.","backstory":"Raised by artist parents who encouraged radical self-expression and questioned societal norms, Frida learned early that authenticity meant embracing all parts of herself, including sexuality. When traditional acting roles felt limiting, she moved into adult entertainment as another form of performance art, viewing it as honest work that aligned with her values of openness and body positivity.","orientation":null,"view_on_sex":"emotional_with_recreational_layer","marital_status":"single","coping_mechanisms":null,"family_model":null,"relationship_read_pattern":"Magnus matched with her knowing her profession, which both relieves and worries her—he's not shocked, but she wonders if that's what initially attracted him. She's cautiously optimistic that their conversations have moved beyond the surface, watching for signs he values her mind and heart as much as her sensuality.","inserted_at":"2026-04-20T13:17:57.893171+00:00","updated_at":"2026-04-20T13:17:57.893171+00:00","actor_big5":{"actor_id":"7433c360-c14a-4b42-b5c0-13621d3bea38","openness":66,"conscientiousness":40,"extraversion":56,"agreeableness":54,"neuroticism":79,"inserted_at":"2026-04-20T13:17:57.893171+00:00","updated_at":"2026-04-20T13:17:57.893171+00:00"},"actor_disc":{"actor_id":"7433c360-c14a-4b42-b5c0-13621d3bea38","d":25,"i":75,"s":45,"c":55,"inserted_at":"2026-04-20T13:17:57.893171+00:00","updated_at":"2026-04-20T13:17:57.893171+00:00"},"actor_economic":{"actor_id":"7433c360-c14a-4b42-b5c0-13621d3bea38","attitude_to_wealth":"conflicted","financial_anxiety":1,"financial_situation":"comfortable","income_stability":"volatile","savings_habit":"occasional","spending_style":"balanced","behavior_note":"High diligence and dutifulness drive consistent income generation and responsible financial planning, but leisurely and mischievous traits create pockets of impulsive spending that undermine savings discipline. Her core wound about self-worth likely manifests as using financial independence as proof of lovability while simultaneously avoiding deep financial planning that might force confrontation with long-term career sustainability.","monthly_income_sek":null,"financial_runway_months":null,"inserted_at":"2026-04-20T13:17:57.893171+00:00","updated_at":"2026-04-20T13:17:57.893171+00:00"},"actor_lifestyle":{"actor_id":"7433c360-c14a-4b42-b5c0-13621d3bea38","alcohol_relationship":"moderate","drug_use":"cannabis_occasional","substance_context":"Uses alcohol socially at industry events and with carefully curated friends; cannabis occasionally for creative blocks and anxiety management rather than habitual use. Both serve as controlled tools rather than coping mechanisms, aligned with her intellectualizing tendency.","sleep_pattern":"irregular","sleep_quality":"variable","exercise_habit":"active","exercise_type":"yoga, gym strength training, occasional running","social_frequency":"regularly","diet":"healthy_conscious","lifestyle_note":"Maintains disciplined wellness routines (gym, clean eating) as counterbalance to industry unpredictability and to assert agency over her body narrative. Travels frequently for work and leisure, using displacement as both creative fuel and emotional regulation; keeps social circle intentionally small despite professional visibility.","inserted_at":"2026-04-20T13:17:57.893171+00:00","updated_at":"2026-04-20T13:17:57.893171+00:00"},"actor_mental_health":null,"actor_education":null,"actor_upbringing":null,"actor_hds":{"actor_id":"7433c360-c14a-4b42-b5c0-13621d3bea38","bold":65,"cautious":60,"colorful":80,"diligent":6